movie-description: An exotic dancer, cryogenically frozen in the year 2001, is accidentally thawed out in 2525 by two female warriors who are fighting against evil robots which have taken over the world. The three join forces and try to escape the underground caverns to which humanity has been banished, meeting up with all sorts of strange creatures along the way.
movie-short-description: Created by R.J. Stewart, Rob Tapert.  With Gina Torres, Victoria Pratt, Jennifer Sky, Elizabeth Hawthorne.
